<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Inter', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f6f9; padding: 40px 0; margin: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; background: white; margin: 0 auto; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #a855f7 100%); padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: white; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
    .content { padding: 30px; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; }
    .message-box { background: #f8fafc; border-left: 4px solid #8b5cf6; padding: 20px; border-radius: 4px; font-style: italic; margin-top: 20px; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #6366f1; color: white !important; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 30px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #888; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>New Message Notification</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hi there!</h2>
      <p>While you were offline, <strong>{{senderUsername}}</strong> sent a new message in your channel!</p>
      
      <div class="message-box">
        "{{messageContent}}"
      </div>

      <center>
        <a href="https://your-chat-app.com/channel/{{channelId}}" class="btn">Open Chat Now</a>
      </center>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      You are receiving this because you were offline when the message was sent.<br>
      © 2026 Chat System Delivery.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
